data.description: Welcome to your exquisite new residence!   Indulge in the sheer opulence of this meticulously maintained 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom townhouse, an absolute haven tailored to your refined tastes. Prepare to be enthralled as you step into the abode, where the luminous floor plan graciously welcomes you, bathed in natural radiance cascading through expansive windows.   The main level unveils an intimate living room, tastefully adorned with a touch of cozy elegance, seamlessly flowing into a separate dining room that exudes sophistication. Prepare delectable culinary delights in the fully equipped kitchen, where culinary excellence meets supreme functionality. Ascend to the upper level and be enraptured by the allure of three resplendent bedrooms, a sanctuary of ultimate tranquility.   The grand master suite, resplendent in its dimensions, beckons with an air of majesty, complete with a lavishly appointed private bathroom and an expansive walk-in closet, ensuring your every need is met with unparalleled elegance.   The remaining two bedrooms, sharing a full bathroom, are no less than enchanting. Nestled discreetly along the upper floor hallway, a hidden gem awaits—the laundry room, effortlessly blending convenience with sophistication. Relish in the splendor of the outdoors on your private patio, a resplendent oasis where relaxation and entertainment meld harmoniously.   In addition, your townhouse provides the coveted convenience of a two-car parking pad, a testament to its commitment to luxury living. This exquisite residence is the culmination of groundbreaking efforts in 2020, resulting in the construction and completion of a masterpiece in 2021.   Do not let this extraordinary opportunity slip through your fingers; seize the chance to lease this resplendent townhouse situated in a prime location, mere moments away from an array of upscale shops, delectable dining establishments, and effortless transportation options. Immerse yourself in the epitome of refined living—schedule your exclusive showing today and embrace the lifestyle you deserve!     Home is currently Tenant Occupied. Tenant can move out with a 60 day notice or can remain as a tenant on property.
